message.body: Do you guys have to be back any certain time Monday? A friend from Vermont is meeting me to camp this weekend, so I'd like to hang out a bit on Monday.
No time restraints here. I figure well give you 20, 30 minutes tops from whatever time you guys meet up and we'll need to hit the road. ...Big Time. Don't worry, I got you Homie.
Haha, right on. I don't want to get back to philly too late. So probably hang out until around lunch time Monday. Should be a grand ol' time
